Cristiano Ronaldo reveals he trusts only four people. Juventus forward, Cristiano Ronaldo, has claimed he only trusts four people in his life. He stated this during an emotional interview with Piers Morgan on ITV. Ronaldo discussed a number of issues in his personal life and outlined how they have affected him, leading to him finding it difficult to trust people. “I’m not going to say names, because I don’t think it is fair. “But I will say, four persons, 100 per cent trust, four persons. “I have very close friends, family, but who I trust 100 per cent, it’s maybe four persons. Life is like that,” Ronaldo said. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.